    "6 was performed, and the three-phase short-circuit level and phasor quantities at the IED bus were computed and processed by the proposed algorithm.To ensure that the set of Monte Carlo scenarios was sufficiently rich in terms of short-circuit levels, a nearestneighbor resolution criterion was applied to the resulting fault currents."
